data.description: Nestled in a serene and desirable neighborhood, this delightful home boasts a NO HOA, NO MUD ,walking distance to Harmony High School, quick access to Highways 59, 6, 8, and 90, it's surrounded by outstanding Fort Bend schools, library, shops, and dining options offer convenience. This property features a generous open floor plan, granite countertops, and consistent tiled/laminate flooring. Revel in the vast backyard, screened-in patio, and an electrified workshop. The extensive covered patio and sizable yard create an ideal outdoor retreat. The converted garage enhances space flexibility. Roof is just 2 years old, new water heater. Schedule a tour today to discover your future home!
